              "lhf_signs",
              "cvs_gpe_findings",
              "precordium_palpation"
            ],
            "description": "Failure of the left ventricle to adequately pump blood. Key features: PND, orthopnea, displaced apex beat, S3 gallop, basal crepitations, raised JVP and peripheral edema in combined failure.",
            "score_rationale": "Symptoms(7) | LHF signs(16) | GPE edema+JVP(4) | displaced apex+LV heave(4) = 29 — broad multi-system presentation"
