            ],
            "description": "Chaotic atrial electrical activity producing an irregularly irregular pulse with variable rate. Pulse deficit (radial rate < auscultated rate) is characteristic. Risk of thromboembolic stroke.",
            "score_rationale": "Irregularly irregular(2)+pulse deficit(2)+tachycardia(1) = 5 — single-fact rhythm diagnosis"
          },
